\begin_layout Subsection
Уточнение функционала
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Ось 
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

 направим вертикально вниз.
 Начальная точка — 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(0;0\right)$
\end_inset

, конечная — 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(x_{1};y_{1}\right).$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Запишем закон сохранения энергии для начальной точки и произвольной точки
 кривой 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(x;y\right)$
\end_inset

:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
0=\frac{mv^{2}}{2}-mgy
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
v^{2}=2gy
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
v=\sqrt{2g}\cdot\sqrt{y}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
v_{y}=v\cdot\sin\alpha
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathrm{tg}\alpha=y^{\prime}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Воспользуемся выражением синуса через тангенс:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sin\alpha=\frac{y^{\prime}}{\sqrt{1+\left(y^{\prime}\right)^{2}}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
v_{y}=\sqrt{2g}\cdot\sqrt{y}\cdot\frac{y^{\prime}}{\sqrt{1+\left(y^{\prime}\right)^{2}}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
T=\intop_{0}^{x_{1}}\frac{y^{\prime}}{\sqrt{2g}\cdot\sqrt{y}\cdot\frac{y^{\prime}}{\sqrt{1+\left(y^{\prime}\right)^{2}}}}dx=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2g}}\intop_{0}^{x_{1}}\frac{\sqrt{1+\left(y^{\prime}\right)^{2}}}{\sqrt{y}}dx.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
L\left(y;y^{\prime};x\right)=\frac{\sqrt{1+\left(y^{\prime}\right)^{2}}}{\sqrt{y}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Дифференциальное уравнение
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial L}{\partial y^{\prime}}y^{\prime}-L=\mathrm{const}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Вычислим необходимую частную производную:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial L}{\partial y^{\prime}}=\frac{1}{\sqrt{y}}\frac{2y^{\prime}}{2\sqrt{1+\left(y^{\prime}\right)^{2}}}=\frac{y^{\prime}}{\sqrt{y}\cdot\sqrt{1+\left(y^{\prime}\right)^{2}}}.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{1}{\sqrt{y}}\frac{y^{\prime}}{\sqrt{1+\left(y^{\prime}\right)^{2}}}y^{\prime}-\frac{\sqrt{1+\left(y^{\prime}\right)^{2}}}{\sqrt{y}}=C
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(y^{\prime}\right)^{2}-\left(1+\left(y^{\prime}\right)^{2}\right)=C\cdot\sqrt{y}\cdot\sqrt{1+\left(y^{\prime}\right)^{2}}.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sqrt{y}\cdot\sqrt{1+\left(y^{\prime}\right)^{2}}=-\frac{1}{C}=A.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Разрешим относительно 
\begin_inset Formula $y^{\prime}$
\end_inset

:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sqrt{1+\left(y^{\prime}\right)^{2}}=\frac{A}{\sqrt{y}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
1+\left(y^{\prime}\right)^{2}=\frac{A^{2}}{y}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
y=\frac{A^{2}}{1+\left(y^{\prime}\right)^{2}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(y^{\prime}\right)^{2}=\frac{A^{2}}{y}-1=\frac{A^{2}-y}{y}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
y^{\prime}=\sqrt{\frac{A^{2}-y}{y}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Решаем дифференциальное уравнение
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
dx=\frac{\sqrt{y}dy}{\sqrt{A^{2}-y}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Произведём замену:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
y=A^{2}\sin^{2}z
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
A^{2}-y=A^{2}\cos^{2}z
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
dy=A^{2}2\sin z\cdot\cos zdz=A^{2}\sin2zdz
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
dx=\frac{A\sin z\cdot A^{2}2\sin z\cdot\cos zdz}{A\cos z}=2A^{2}\sin^{2}zdz
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
В результате замены получим:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
dx=2A^{2}\frac{1-\cos2z}{2}dz=A^{2}\left(1-\cos2z\right)dz
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Проинтегрируем:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
x+B=A^{2}\left(z-\frac{1}{2}\sin2z\right)=A^{2}\left(z-\sin z\cdot\cos z\right)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
y=A^{2}\frac{1-\cos2z}{2}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\cos2z=1-\frac{2y}{A^{2}}=\frac{A^{2}-2y}{A^{2}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
z=\frac{1}{2}\arccos\frac{A^{2}-2y}{A^{2}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sin z\cdot\cos z=\sqrt{\frac{y}{A^{2}}\frac{\left(A^{2}-y\right)}{A^{2}}}=\frac{\sqrt{y\left(A^{2}-y\right)}}{A^{2}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
x+B=A^{2}\left(\frac{1}{2}\arccos\frac{A^{2}-2y}{A^{2}}-\frac{\sqrt{y\left(A^{2}-y\right)}}{A^{2}}\right)=\frac{A^{2}}{2}\arccos\frac{A^{2}-2y}{A^{2}}-\sqrt{y\left(A^{2}-y\right)}.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Уравнения движения
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
dt=\frac{dy}{v_{y}}=\frac{y^{\prime}}{v_{y}}dx
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
v_{y}=\frac{y^{\prime}\sqrt{2gy}}{\sqrt{1+\left(y^{\prime}\right)^{2}}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
dt=\frac{y^{\prime}\cdot\sqrt{1+\left(y^{\prime}\right)^{2}}}{y^{\prime}\sqrt{2gy}}dx=\frac{\sqrt{1+\left(y^{\prime}\right)^{2}}}{\sqrt{2gy}}dx
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
y^{\prime}=\sqrt{\frac{A^{2}-y}{y}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(y^{\prime}\right)^{2}=\frac{A^{2}-y}{y}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
1+\left(y^{\prime}\right)^{2}=1+\frac{A^{2}-y}{y}=\frac{A^{2}}{y}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
dt=\frac{A}{\sqrt{y}\cdot\sqrt{2gy}}dx=\frac{A}{\sqrt{2g}\cdot y}dx
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
dx=\frac{\sqrt{y}dy}{\sqrt{A^{2}-y}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
dt=\frac{A}{\sqrt{2g}}\cdot\frac{\sqrt{y}dy}{y\sqrt{A^{2}-y}}=\frac{A}{\sqrt{2g}}\cdot\frac{dy}{\sqrt{y\left(A^{2}-y\right)}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
y=A^{2}\sin^{2}z
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sqrt{y\left(A^{2}-y\right)}=\sqrt{A^{2}\sin^{2}z\cdot A^{2}\cos^{2}z}=\frac{A^{2}}{2}\sqrt{\sin^{2}2z}=\frac{A^{2}\sin2z}{2}.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
dt=\frac{A}{\sqrt{2g}}\cdot\frac{2A^{2}\sin2zdz}{A^{2}\sin2z}=\sqrt{\frac{2A^{2}}{g}}\cdot dz
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
t+a=\sqrt{\frac{2A^{2}}{g}}\cdot z
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
z=\sqrt{\frac{g}{2A^{2}}}\cdot\left(t+a\right)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
